cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper deals with the generation of filter lists for web resource blocking, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of deep browser instrumentation and an ad classifier, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM).
